{
  "voice_id": "7kXNOCqiaLdszL0OEXks",
  "model_id": "eleven_multilingual_v2",
  "voice_settings": {
    "stability": 0.65,
    "similarity_boost": 0.65,
    "style": 0.0,
    "speed": 1.1,
    "use_speaker_boost": true
  },
  "pronunciation_dictionary_locators": [
    {
      "pronunciation_dictionary_id": "AhK3J8mZDRoShxfoJLk6",
      "version_id": "pFvyQBbxEBKyF7C3IHpy"
    }
  ],
  "inter_chunk_silence_ms": 650,
  "chunks": [
    {
      "index": 0,
      "text": "You can make a video by writing HTML. No React.",
      "checksum": "sha256:d834e8496e767e98f6718eaef4a82368fbec003c96981595e37ae13326643b4e",
      "wav": "chunk-00.wav",
      "duration": 3.2043537414965986,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 0
    },
    {
      "index": 1,
      "text": "No build step. In this tutorial we go from zero to a rendered MP4 \u2014 Windows, macOS, or Linux.",
      "checksum": "sha256:e6c24c3d474ef05bb75ebc3e7aaa46dbaf5fa1c7af51c6d6545926ba643746e8",
      "wav": "chunk-01.wav",
      "duration": 7.244625850340136,
      "word_count": 19,
      "words_offset": 10
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "text": "The official quickstart is at hyperframes.heygen.com slash quickstart.",
      "checksum": "sha256:60290ac4aba27980a20beaa01a9d606e57acf24feb92be8448ab34269781e152",
      "wav": "chunk-02.wav",
      "duration": 4.504671201814059,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 29
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "text": "We're walking through every step on screen.",
      "checksum": "sha256:b227fc08b61f38d2a93c374360ddf10387713c617f6854106a9ccad55bfabb88",
      "wav": "chunk-03.wav",
      "duration": 2.414875283446712,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 37
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "text": "Two hard requirements. Node.js twenty-two or higher.",
      "checksum": "sha256:18e55a1c3614bd7e840afba2c30a87218a70e0a8149e4e32e04b701aebfe2bc8",
      "wav": "chunk-04.wav",
      "duration": 3.3901133786848074,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 44
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "text": "FFmpeg seven or higher. Docker is optional.",
      "checksum": "sha256:3624de9230c655f68ae030525c79a301d9bd2048f3f9a99eef437da553761130",
      "wav": "chunk-05.wav",
      "duration": 2.786394557823129,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 51
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "text": "Everything else \u2014 the studio, the renderer, the templates \u2014 comes through one npx command.",
      "checksum": "sha256:8dd28c6f187d95020bec81827d1696499713c6a1289b00cfe1116237e7fbc6e3",
      "wav": "chunk-06.wav",
      "duration": 5.6656689342403626,
      "word_count": 15,
      "words_offset": 58
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "text": "Step one. Node twenty-two. Go to nodejs.org slash download.",
      "checksum": "sha256:a0229f624f1264df391561292cad3833d814646cf9acc450c8ebb50ee224e3c4",
      "wav": "chunk-07.wav",
      "duration": 4.876190476190477,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 73
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "text": "The page detects your OS. Windows \u2014 grab the dot-msi or run winget install OpenJS dot Nodejs dot LTS.",
      "checksum": "sha256:fe02634acbfb27a425f5486b39fe6baf8d30ffca48b0d32c2f19d5aaee4e2204",
      "wav": "chunk-08.wav",
      "duration": 8.870022675736962,
      "word_count": 19,
      "words_offset": 82
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "text": "Linux or macOS \u2014 use nvm so you can swap versions per project.",
      "checksum": "sha256:abf98fdea583d4df8853d06b60bf43e9642e8fe634c8c8dc3fc4a017c0b902fa",
      "wav": "chunk-09.wav",
      "duration": 4.4117913832199545,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 101
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "text": "Step two. FFmpeg seven. Go to ffmpeg.org slash download.",
      "checksum": "sha256:31d0c5b8c00eb61f4c75c900b862983f810a894189a882a043ae22060c7b5ef1",
      "wav": "chunk-10.wav",
      "duration": 4.6439909297052155,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 114
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "text": "Windows \u2014 winget install ffmpeg. Linux \u2014 apt install ffmpeg. macOS \u2014 brew install ffmpeg.",
      "checksum": "sha256:15f0971922601dcceae674ee43bca4e7214d4f365112e845d8e5aeba7c5fffd6",
      "wav": "chunk-11.wav",
      "duration": 7.75546485260771,
      "word_count": 15,
      "words_offset": 123
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "text": "Sanity check. Two commands. node minus minus version. ffmpeg minus version.",
      "checksum": "sha256:9fea215980fe68898c46b97d57dc399b6a9bf45b4a6675b736788e5984c8902d",
      "wav": "chunk-12.wav",
      "duration": 5.526349206349207,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 138
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "text": "If they print, you're done with prereqs.",
      "checksum": "sha256:d78e44514fb214ade15afb91fa074d001202e3934555d7a371d34a73999611d4",
      "wav": "chunk-13.wav",
      "duration": 2.182675736961451,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 149
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "text": "If not, reopen your terminal so PATH refreshes.",
      "checksum": "sha256:b7054008cdd17503b7c517bcfd725576575ac04e9f77f7672f07e0f6bd033a96",
      "wav": "chunk-14.wav",
      "duration": 2.9257142857142857,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 156
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "text": "Pick a code agent. HyperFrames was built for AI agents to drive.",
      "checksum": "sha256:dfe494ef30e719126c0363e4907878119bb63e17855f3c41abbebd9d99b86e83",
      "wav": "chunk-15.wav",
      "duration": 4.179591836734694,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 164
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "text": "Two picks. Claude Code by Anthropic \u2014 install via the native installer, not npm.",
      "checksum": "sha256:07a7a8cef932b406dc2187c6aeb0bf29b82fd8391c541914f17d4835d4a4822d",
      "wav": "chunk-16.wav",
      "duration": 5.340589569160998,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 176
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "text": "Or OpenAI's Codex CLI \u2014 npm install, dash g, at openai slash codex.",
      "checksum": "sha256:e032da795365ef95457c9b5bfdd09ad4eca59e3adb9598ef0f78ce346c99c02e",
      "wav": "chunk-17.wav",
      "duration": 6.176507936507937,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 190
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "text": "Either works. Teach your agent HyperFrames.",
      "checksum": "sha256:38e46c137b5d298dc72f79dd1a59f27f0e53d28c264b294fbe71cd24e386f5c7",
      "wav": "chunk-18.wav",
      "duration": 2.8792743764172335,
      "word_count": 6,
      "words_offset": 203
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "text": "One npx command: npx skills add heygen-com slash hyperframes.",
      "checksum": "sha256:44b4e7a6bceef1fd9f0397976d1ce2ebdaaad9d202a013aaa387c0d2fa888c26",
      "wav": "chunk-19.wav",
      "duration": 4.2260317460317465,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 209
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "text": "Five skills install. Spawn a project. npx hyperframes init my-video.",
      "checksum": "sha256:01cd91b9f41e945e47c51330060b0f5dddfbef60b52d858498d8c9c098a262b4",
      "wav": "chunk-20.wav",
      "duration": 4.458231292517007,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 218
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "text": "Pick a starter from the interactive picker.",
      "checksum": "sha256:6568e1147f4c867bac7cedcd8750f72c1ff6d4b8c6e92bd46bcf2e9d02fa2a77",
      "wav": "chunk-21.wav",
      "duration": 2.414875283446712,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 228
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "text": "Blank, Warm Grain, Swiss Grid, Vignelli, NYT Graph, and more.",
      "checksum": "sha256:db231096ab45d4786a7d7439690e83134226a248214f8e84788f8ebd46408ae5",
      "wav": "chunk-22.wav",
      "duration": 4.133151927437642,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 235
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "text": "Hit enter, six files appear, then a Get-Started guide.",
      "checksum": "sha256:7d7bcb834a8e9f259c6387c87b5400b52c6cd7928ee6a5df1d7766204a7a89dd",
      "wav": "chunk-23.wav",
      "duration": 3.3436734693877552,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 245
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "text": "Open the project with your agent. cd my-video, then run claude.",
      "checksum": "sha256:271d17653dd8174a6acb13937689557c53af1d2143109011729c45a20a66a32d",
      "wav": "chunk-24.wav",
      "duration": 3.9938321995464854,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 254
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "text": "It auto-loads the HyperFrames skills, so it knows the framework's patterns before you type a thing.",
      "checksum": "sha256:da966e3619ca87c845c22312134274a767be210b9ea55158a0f6bdf41f017baa",
      "wav": "chunk-25.wav",
      "duration": 5.479909297052155,
      "word_count": 16,
      "words_offset": 265
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "text": "Tell it what you want. Using slash hyperframes, create a five-second intro that says Hello HyperFrames with a fade-in.",
      "checksum": "sha256:d3e25c2f3c4ec6df0fe3b9f63b23b7dbe1545b935b7118c1d72e7270c35f32a5",
      "wav": "chunk-26.wav",
      "duration": 6.965986394557823,
      "word_count": 19,
      "words_offset": 281
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "text": "The agent reads the skill, then edits index dot html for you.",
      "checksum": "sha256:6732a9114922c2dac0541de17062ecf9db1fdea4f9a4496c7c37ce4e2473701d",
      "wav": "chunk-27.wav",
      "duration": 3.3901133786848074,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 300
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "text": "Run npx hyperframes preview in another terminal.",
      "checksum": "sha256:ec158b262168ecf337493a26bca56ca6e2d88ff35c4835e4193dfc08e291816b",
      "wav": "chunk-28.wav",
      "duration": 2.9257142857142857,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 312
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "text": "The studio opens in your browser. Every time the agent saves, the canvas reloads.",
      "checksum": "sha256:4a5ebcb091dfeb529093fa3937abf28d44d99ab7fc84bf2a556a53bbd2a0d3e4",
      "wav": "chunk-29.wav",
      "duration": 4.73687074829932,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 319
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "text": "Here's our first result \u2014 clean, centered, fading in.",
      "checksum": "sha256:3c17a8b108ae9e6d4625147de5921144e0ffa3871a8227705d0fbae2a0063baf",
      "wav": "chunk-30.wav",
      "duration": 3.297233560090703,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 333
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "text": "Want changes? Just ask. Make the title bigger, and add a subtitle: Made with HyperFrames.",
      "checksum": "sha256:727716a7fedc3c71c4b63bc5d07a1f8763cfac8a5f10240273c99e83bbbbd4a5",
      "wav": "chunk-31.wav",
      "duration": 5.944308390022676,
      "word_count": 15,
      "words_offset": 342
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "text": "The agent rewrites the file. The studio reloads.",
      "checksum": "sha256:e4a793b665b6f705bb81c3dafe0fbc603810115814e7804ad34a279860d9182e",
      "wav": "chunk-32.wav",
      "duration": 2.972154195011338,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 357
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "text": "No build step, no rebuild loop. Iteration two.",
      "checksum": "sha256:497916c72f8d99fb005f183b35844ecb583b4b04222128c7f9f9eabae7e369db",
      "wav": "chunk-33.wav",
      "duration": 2.9257142857142857,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 365
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "text": "Bigger title. Subtitle below. Same five-second intro, in seconds, by talking to your agent.",
      "checksum": "sha256:15b2977a04c1dca402e0cf6104f5476ad9b082ddf5fe948b852748ac95ff0780",
      "wav": "chunk-34.wav",
      "duration": 5.479909297052155,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 373
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "text": "Before rendering, check it. npx hyperframes check.",
      "checksum": "sha256:48db4306f90afaa1b6cf465579b65ae3743bde926cc714c67a824d35f4559c80",
      "wav": "chunk-35.wav",
      "duration": 3.250793650793651,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 387
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "text": "It runs lint, validate, and inspect. Lint catches missing data attributes.",
      "checksum": "sha256:07bbfb1612e127a8535903861c941e041d9d5f415f9706c58cc352c8a2336c02",
      "wav": "chunk-36.wav",
      "duration": 4.272471655328798,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 394
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "text": "Validate runs WCAG contrast in headless Chrome.",
      "checksum": "sha256:45574f6aea3016bc09e5052d8bf42a807518130a35e42b0406c8e30a010242df",
      "wav": "chunk-37.wav",
      "duration": 3.250793650793651,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 405
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "text": "Inspect checks for layout overflow. Zero errors means you're good to render.",
      "checksum": "sha256:4048ec4ab49c26a91bc60783380d7cc0be2cd9bdf299fd70dea7d092a789ddd3",
      "wav": "chunk-38.wav",
      "duration": 4.2260317460317465,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 412
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "text": "Then render. npx hyperframes render. Headless Chromium boots.",
      "checksum": "sha256:bb698362922e31667823378159e5a095bc2a81a3f88fde43090f709fc4556be3",
      "wav": "chunk-39.wav",
      "duration": 3.947392290249433,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 424
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "text": "The Frame Adapter pauses time. Frames step deterministically.",
      "checksum": "sha256:4fc022f74d84bab9c72674b7430a32a548ce553e27acd29acd6473126d94b604",
      "wav": "chunk-40.wav",
      "duration": 4.133151927437642,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 432
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "text": "FFmpeg encodes the MP4. A five-second clip renders in about six seconds.",
      "checksum": "sha256:71c49cc995b5b1d105fab9a91e2972b0a1e679bc639e97745207f85a60fa58e9",
      "wav": "chunk-41.wav",
      "duration": 5.526349206349207,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 440
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "text": "That's the full pipeline. Node, FFmpeg, an agent, init, prompt, preview, check, render.",
      "checksum": "sha256:09ad0fd69121c9dc884c952aba78558b2b6729b070ba4bdbf1ff9cdab5e9f94a",
      "wav": "chunk-42.wav",
      "duration": 6.362267573696145,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 452
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "text": "All open source. So tell me \u2014 what kind of video would you build first?",
      "checksum": "sha256:eff4387e8bbffa19a88c066156243cd0ee4172fde7a0282bd0121fcebe7bda4d",
      "wav": "chunk-43.wav",
      "duration": 4.551111111111111,
      "word_count": 15,
      "words_offset": 465
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "text": "A title card, a tutorial, a product demo, something else?",
      "checksum": "sha256:e7be2c7b4f25413dff0503454f591091129b610874b34a0e008f6c02f4dcee62",
      "wav": "chunk-44.wav",
      "duration": 3.297233560090703,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 480
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "text": "Drop your idea in the comments. Links in the description.",
      "checksum": "sha256:78ed1e969b8c0c7b928ce047a15fdbdc13fa08c1d48a30be1a75276c7bb38038",
      "wav": "chunk-45.wav",
      "duration": 3.3436734693877552,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 490
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "text": "Subscribe for more.",
      "checksum": "sha256:1dedcd7e8327664a6fa24822d99bbdc110575e0796986aa2468645046a2dffc5",
      "wav": "chunk-46.wav",
      "duration": 1.3003174603174603,
      "word_count": 3,
      "words_offset": 500
    }
  ]
}